section.section:
Of the amount provided from the Racetrack Facility Renewal Account under subsection (d)(1) of this section, the racecourse at Timonium shall be provided the following amounts for racetrack facility capital construction and improvements:
for fiscal year 2012, $1,125,000;
for fiscal year 2013, $1,250,000;
for fiscal year 2014, $1,125,000;
for fiscal year 2015, $1,000,000; and
for fiscal year 2016, $1,000,000.
